      <title>Christmas Update v7.1.0</title>
      <pubDate>Friday, 10 Dec 2021</pubDate>
      <description>
	&lt;h1&gt;Happy Hollidays!&lt;/h1&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;Updates to P.E.T. have been made to keep up with the new updates belonging to the new Christmas update.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;h1&gt;ADDITIONS&lt;/h1&gt;
	&lt;ul class=&quot;bb_ul&quot;&gt;
	  &lt;li&gt;Added ghost type: The Mimic.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	  &lt;li&gt;The Evidence page now works around The Mimic (since The Mimic now has a fourth potential evidence -- the Ghost Orb).&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	  &lt;li&gt;Added translations for all Ghosts and Evidence.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	  &lt;li&gt;New layout format and font appearance within data-centric pages.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;h1&gt;FIXES&lt;/h1&gt;
	&lt;ul class=&quot;bb_ul&quot;&gt;
	  &lt;li&gt;Made optimization for layouts to better fit all devices.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	  &lt;li&gt;Fixed all bugs found with the Phase Timer.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	  &lt;li&gt;Further optimized a lot of code.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	  &lt;li&gt;Fixed bugs with the Phase Timer.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
      </description>
    </item>
    <item>
